abstract: >-
  GAUNTLEX runs concurrent Builder and Breaker AI agents against the same
  specification, producing an Adversarial Resilience Score that gates CI
  for AI-generated code across OWASP Top 10, HIPAA, FINRA, PCI DSS, and
  SOC 2 domains.
